data.description: Investors and developers come have a look! This great opportunity in South Hill could be the perfect fix and flip, sub-divide, or new construction site. Or get creative and use the 4500 SF for an adult family home, or communal living space. The large .69 acre lot is full of potential for the right buyer. The location is ideal as its located between Puyallup and South Hill with great access to the freeway, shopping and entertainment, yet a nice and safe neighborhood vibe. Property being sold as-is and not bank financeable. Buyer to verify all information.
